@DATABASE "Deathzone"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - D - Deathzone"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - D
                   ====================================

                                 Deathzone
                                 =========


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" rxs "address command zxampoke(60149,0)"}          60149,0
@{"Lives = x     " rxs "address command zxampoke(59193,255)"}          59133,x (x= 1-255)
@{"Level = x     " rxs "address command zxampoke(59198,1)"}          59198,x (x= 1-4)

                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs - Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
